  (text "BACKPLANE (docs/09 s.2): near-passive. Bus entry: lugs -> 250uOhm bar shunt\n(placeholder fp; real bar at the PCB pass) -> INA228 high-side meter (0x40 on\nthe manager-local I2C; pull-ups live on the manager). E-stop: 3V3 THROUGH the\nNC panel switch -> 1K -> HW_EN; broken wire / unplugged manager = all SAFE.\nCAN: 120R at both physical ends; manager is a stub. Slot straps: grounded pin\n= bit set (fw board.h SLOT_ID_IN inverts) -> slot 0 = all open."
    (at 342.9 261.62 0)
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)))
    (uuid a2f71080-7586-4648-889b-954f66cc1d95)
  )

